Michael McCullers -LRB- born 1971 -RRB- is an American comedy film screenwriter .
A native of Indian Springs Village , Alabama , McCullers attended Indian Springs School , a private high school just south of Birmingham , Alabama .
McCullers is a former writer on Saturday Night Live and is best known for co-writing the script for two Austin Powers movies , Austin Powers : The Spy Who Shagged Me and Austin Powers in Goldmember with Mike Myers .
He is the writer and director of the 2008 comedy Baby Mama starring Tina Fey and Amy Poehler .
He lives in Los Angeles with his wife and four children .